---
import "@design-system/styles/color.css";

const title = "Pelilauta Design System";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title}</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <p class="eyebrow">PELILAUTA / V21</p>
      <h1>{title}</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        Living books connect design intent to the exact contracts used by
        Pelilauta. Each book is shipped with its specification and production
        implementation.
      </p>
      <section>
        <p class="index">01 / COLOR SYSTEM</p>
        <h2><a href="/tokens/color">Light and Dark color themes</a></h2>
        <p>
          The established v20 OKLCH references, semantic roles, and Cyan 4
          compatibility contract now loaded by <code>pelilauta.social</code>.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <p class="index">02 / ICONOGRAPHY</p>
        <h2><a href="/iconography">Using icons in Pelilauta</a></h2>
        <p>
          Usage principles, do's and don'ts, and the available icon vocabulary
          grouped by purpose. The <a href="/components/icon">Icon component book</a>
          covers how a single icon renders.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :global(*) {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  :global(body) {
    margin: 0;
    min-block-size: 100vh;
    color: var(--cn-text);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 10%, var(--cn-hover), transparent 35rem),
      var(--cn-background);
    font-family: "Avenir Next", Avenir, system-ui, sans-serif;
  }
  main {
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 7rem) clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    max-inline-size: 72rem;
  }
  .eyebrow,
  .index {
    color: var(--cn-text-low);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  }
  h1 {
    margin-block: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    max-inline-size: 10ch;
    color: var(--cn-text-high);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 9vw, 7rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
    line-height: 0.88;
  }
  .intro {
    max-inline-size: 42rem;
    color: var(--cn-text-low);
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  section {
    margin-block-start: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 10rem);
    padding-block-start: 1.5rem;
    border-block-start: 1px solid var(--cn-border);
  }
  h2 {
    margin-block: 1rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 3.25rem);
  }
  a {
    color: var(--cn-link);
    text-decoration-thickness: 0.08em;
    text-underline-offset: 0.15em;
  }
  a:hover {
    color: var(--cn-link-hover);
  }
  code {
    color: var(--cn-text-high);
  }
</style>
